game.name: Princess Urban Outfitters Autumn
game.description:
Autumn season is just around the corner and your favorite Disney characters including two villains named the Evil Queen and Maleficent and two princesses named Tiana and Elsa want to greet it in a new fashion style. They need new outfits before entering the town so they have decided to rush towards the most popular fashion store named Urban Outfitters to shop for their desired dresses and accessories. Join Princess Urban Outfitters Autumn to guide them to shop for the perfect fall outfits! 

Choose layering shirts with some fuzzy coats and cozy sweaters with a combination of a right skirt or a pair of matching pants, and chick knee-tall boots for this season in this HTML5 dressing game! Put your fashion abilities and style sense to the test to help all the four to pick up the best outfits for their upcoming shopping spree! Start with Maleficent by giving her a knitted outfit and pairing it with a cool jacket, a matching handbag and a pair of leather boots!

Choose the turtleneck blouses for the Queen Elsa for this season and pair it with a denim skirt or colored pants with a cute pair of ankle boots and a wonderful suit jacket in this new fashion game! Then dress up Tiana with some playful prints and look fabulous for the outing. A bra top along with some colorful leggings and some tall boots will be a perfect look for the Evil Queen. Do not forget to complete her look with a colorful handbag and a faux fur coat. Enjoy many funny dress-up challenges for free on atmegame.com, no download required!
